The '''E 371''' is part of the [[United Nations]] [[international E-road network]]. Approximately {{convert|358|km|mi|sp=us}} long, it runs from [[Radom]], [[Poland]] south to [[Prešov]], [[Slovakia]].<ref>[http://www.unece.org/trans/doc/2002/sc1agr/TRANS-SC1-AC5-2002-03e.pdf European Agreement on Main International Traffic Arteries], 5 April 2002</ref>

The E 371 follows the route [[Radom]] - [[Ostrowiec Świętokrzyski]] - [[Tarnobrzeg]] - [[Rzeszów]] - [[Barwinek, Podkarpackie Voivodeship|Barwinek]] - [[Vyšný Komárnik]] - [[Svidník]] - [[Giraltovce]] - [[Prešov]]

